{"tid":2027650,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[ViuTV 8:30]Hotel del luna德魯納酒店 (16) 大海很漂亮 但漂亮得很悲傷","createTime":"2020-05-21T12:55:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T13:16:37.000Z","uid":157617,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"68d66d771159a8bfc60f982697307b4c0f759070","tid":2027650,"uid":157617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T12:55:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vxt2Chg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVxt2Chg.jpg&h=75d2e5f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JjAgGJX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJjAgGJX.jpg&h=91ac20dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主演:<br />\n李知恩(IU)，呂珍九，申正根，裴海善，表志勳(Block B P.O)，康美娜(Gugudan Mina)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2019年，首爾市內變化最大的市中心正中間，位置於黃金寶地 &mdash; 明洞的古老破舊建築物，乍一看就像準備重建的空建築物，但仔細地看的話，其實是經營中的酒店。<br />\n<br />\n如果早上的話，在那前面有數百萬的流動人口經過，卻幾乎沒有客人進入那酒店裡面。而在開始入夜、路上變得更冷清、市中心也入睡之時，招牌便亮著燈光，酒店樓層亦會升高的....德魯納酒店。<br />\n<br />\n靈賓專用的德魯納酒店裡，超精英酒店管理人具燦星擔任著總經理，和乖戾、脾氣暴躁的社長張滿月一起，為特別的靈魂客人們提供特級服務時發生的故事。<br />\n<br />\n社長ig<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/fullmoon.long/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ffullmoon.long%2F&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoVwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=a5932613\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/fullmoon.long/</a><br />\n<br />\nFull OST: <br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pFSHBdNoHqM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpFSHBdNoHqM&d=%2FbZU6AtRr1oB2SY8YhhoVwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=adfa9c49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pFSHBdNoHqM</a>"},{"pid":"a537d3363722ea0958f45dff4d76eb24a3d2f199","tid":2027650,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T13:02:40.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n正評！"},{"pid":"d95cc6861d9b215962f07b4439bb9a2f4abe96a8","tid":2027650,"uid":157617,"like":0,"dislike":0